If "<OS$Version>" = "" Then Obey
RMEnsure FontManager 2.89 Obey
FontInstall <Obey$Dir>.
If OS$Version >= 400 Then FontInstall Resources:$.Fonts.

| If we're booting over the network and the font isn't in ROM, copy it...
SetEval LocalFont 0
IfThere Resources:$.Fonts.Caius Then Else SetEval LocalFont LocalFont+1
If "<Obey$Dir>" LEFT 10 <> "Resources:" Then SetEval LocalFont LocalFont+1
If LocalFont > 1 Then Run <Obey$Dir>.CopyLocal
Unset LocalFont
